              <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>Do employers accept online bachelor's degrees?</summary>
                <p>Yes. The stigma around online degrees has largely disappeared, especially since the COVID-19 pandemic normalized remote work and learning. Most employers focus on accreditation status and institutional reputation rather than delivery format.</p>
              </details>
