          <section id="conclusion">
            <div class="section-label">Conclusion</div>
            <h2>The Right Affordable Degree Is Within Reach</h2>

            <p>An affordable online bachelor's degree from a reputable institution is one of the most powerful investments you can make in your future. With programs starting under $300 per credit at accredited schools like SNHU, ASU Online, and WGU, the barrier to entry has never been lower.</p>

            <p>The key is to prioritize accreditation, evaluate your transfer credit options, and choose a program aligned with your career goals. Whether you're pursuing business administration, psychology, or another field, the schools featured in this guide offer a proven combination of quality, flexibility, and affordability.</p>

